item.title: CVE-2021-42068|2024-08-04T03:22:25.961Z -- sap%20se -- sap%203d%20visual%20enterprise%20viewer
item.description: When a user opens a manipulated GIF (.gif) file received from untrusted sources in SAP 3D Visual Enterprise Viewer - version 9.0, the application crashes and becomes temporarily unavailable to the user until restart of the application.
